Hey,

Just a reminder that I’m a Personal stylist & shopper!! Yes I post looks on insta to give you an insight into my style & some fashion inspo!! But mostly you’ll find me in a store with a client or doing a wardrobe edit at a clients home!! Sometimes I’m on fashion shoots & sometimes styling online helping my clients with everything from event styling to the everyday. 

If you’ve been thinking of working with a stylist I’d love to hear from you.  It’s fun & I guarantee you’ll feel a lot more confident when we’re done.  Happy Wednesday you beauts Kelly xxx
